# Full Pages Copy Workflow

Use this rule when the user asks to copy or bring over a page from `full.ssgm.app`.

- `full.ssgm.app` is the reference source for full page UI.
- `ssgm.app` and this repository are the target app.
- Copy the page as-is as closely as practical.
- Match layout, sections, tabs, labels, visuals, and placeholder/static values from the reference page.
- It is acceptable for the copied page to be blank or static after the copy.
- Do not proactively implement real data wiring, backend routes, mutations, persistence, or CRUD unless the user explicitly asks for that later.
- Keep changes surgical. Do not refactor unrelated code while doing a page copy.
